# oude_versie_default_help

  Type "help commands" for a list of general commands
  Type "help parameters" for a list of all parameters setting command
  Type "help other" for a list of other 'helpable' items

  Type "help <item>" for more information on a specific <item>

  in the explanatory text the symbols | and [] are used.
  |  indicates alternatives, like in     size landscape | portrait
  [] indicates optional text, like in    plot [i[nteractive]]

